text: I go to sleep thinking about you. I wake up thinking about you. Whatever I do, I think of you. I just can't seem to get you out of my mind.
I always tell myself I'm going to bed early but it never actually happens.
I want to explore the world. Camera in one hand, and the other hand holding you close.
I can't help but feel so attached.
You are the risk I’ll always take.
Falling in love is easy. Staying in love is a special thing.
I want to run away with you, where there is only you and me.
Sometimes I just wanna tell you everything. How I feel about you, how much you mean to me, how much care about you and how much I love you.
The more people I meet, the more I realize that it's only you I want to be with.
I always wonder if you smile at my texts like I smile at yours.
I just want to have a place in your heart like you have a place in mine.
I love you even when I hate you.
What hurts the most is seeing the person you love, loving someone else right in front of you.
No one sees you like I do.
The truth is, if I could be with anyone, I would still choose you.
We are not given a good life or a bad life. We are given a life. It's up to us to make it good or bad.
I don't think you have any idea how easily you make me smile.
I like your face, that's why I stare.
Be different.
Respect is always both ways.
True friends are like diamonds: precious and rare. Fake friends are like leaves you can find everywhere.
If two people are meant to be together, someday they will find a way.
Smiling does not necessarily mean you're happy. Sometimes it just means you're strong.
Will it be easy? Nope. Will it be worth it? Absolutely.
Never change who you are just because somebody else has a problem with it.
Never let success get to your head and never let failure get to your heart.
Things change, people change. Don't forget the past save good memories.
There are so many people out there who will tell you that you can't, but all you have to do is turn around and say. Watch me.
S.M.I.L.E. [S]howing [M]iracles [I]n [L]ittle [E]fforts
Never let the sadness of your past and the fear of your future ruin the happiness of your present.
Beauty gets the attention but personality gets the heart.
Every girl is beautiful. You just need to find the right guy to see it.
Good friends are hard to find, even harder to leave and impossible to forget.
Bad days will pass and become past.
I really do just want you to be happy. But if there is any way I could be that happiness, just let me know.
She turned her can'ts into cans and her dreams into plans.
Surround yourself with positive people.
They told me that to make him fall in love I had to make him laugh. But everytime he laughs I'm the one who falls in love.
I just wanna make art, read books and find someone who likes me enough.
I believe in the person I want to become.
There are reasons why we have bad days.
Good things are going to happen.
Truth is, I am really in love with you.
Life is so confusing, like one day you're the happiest person ever and tomorrow you just hate everyone and everything for no logical reason
You need to treat her well, if you want to keep her forever.
I admit that I get jealous when you are talking to someone else instead of me.
Once I get you, I don't plan on losing you.
Miles mean nothing when the person that is miles away means everything.
What comes easy, won't last. What lasts, won't come easy.
You're more perfect than anyone else I've met.
Can I curl up in your arms? Fall asleep? With you holding me close? Because you are the only thing that makes me feel safe.
Your voice, to me, it's better than all my favorite songs.
Love isn't suppose to be easy, it is supposed to be worth it.
I like my bed, but I'd rather be in yours.
He ignores you but you like him. He does nothing yet you fall for him. You miss him, but he never thought about you.
The most beautiful thing is to see the person you love smiling and even more beautiful is, knowing that you are the reason behind it.
That relationship where you can talk all the way from "good morning" to "good night" and never get bored of each other.
You asked me how I was doing and I lied and said I was fine. I mean, life is okay, but it would be better if you were mine.
Saying you'll never fall in love is like saying you'll never smile. No matter how hard you try, someone will come along and make you.
Late night conversations make you learn a lot about someone.
The more we talk, the more I fall.
You're the one, the one I was looking for.
A good boyfriend can’t fix all of your problems, but he can promise you that you won’t have to face them alone.
Just hearing the sound of your voice can completely turn my day around.
I love you. Don't ever think that I don't and don't ever forget that I do.
You may be out of my sight, but never out of my mind.
Your smile is amazing, your hugs are warming, your hands are so protective, you're perfect to me.
When you really love someone, stupid conversations make sense.
Sometimes the more you get to know a person, the more attractive they become.
Best thing a man would do for his lady is to prove his love for her.
When I tell you that I love you, I don't say it out of habit. I say to remind you that you're the best thing that's ever happened to me.
I try to fool myself. I try to pretend that I want someone else. But deep down, I know that I always wish for you.
She wants a boy who will stay up late, just to talk to her.
Even if you push them away, people who truly love you will always choose to stay.
The longer the wait, the sweeter the kiss.
"I'm fine." = I wish you knew how I feel inside.
Call me greedy, call me selfish, but I don't want anyone else to hold your hand.
For some reasons, my heart beats out of my chest when I see you.
The world seems like a better place when we are together. Everything becomes more beautiful.
Dear crush, I've fallen so hopelessly in love with you. Your eyes, your laugh, your eyes, your smile, everything about you.
I couldn't imagine having anything more than you. You're my best friend. You're everything to me. Obviously I don't want anything else.
Me and you? I want that. A lot.
The next time I fall in love, I want someone who will make me feel that loving him is the best decision and not just another mistake.
If I'm in a relationship with you, trust me when I say there is no one else I'd rather be with.
Today I caught myself smiling for no reason, then I realized I was thinking about you.
I bet not even all the fireworks in the world can light up my world like you do.
Don't feel sad when someone gave up on you. Feel sorry for them because they gave up on someone who would have never given up on them.
I'm glad I met you. Now do me a favor and stay.
I want a guy who will see me wearing sweats, hair messy, and no makeup and the first thing he says is, “damn you look beautiful.”
I miss you. It’s just another way of saying “I love you enough to want you here with me."
I wish I could spend every moment of the day with you.
I want to love someone who keeps on insisting to be with me, even if I'm mad, even if I'm not in the mood, and even if they're busy.
I don’t have the prettiest face for you to look at or the skinniest waist for you to hold, but I do have the biggest heart to love you with.
I get the best feeling in the world every time you say hi and smile at me.
Falling in love is easy, but staying in love is very special.
I fell in love with someone I never expected to fall for.
Forget the rest, you're the only one I need.
You could talk about anything. I'd still listen because I love hearing your voice.
Words can never describe how special you are to me, but all I can say is, my world is full of smiles whenever I think of you.
I am scared to see someone else with you.
What is love? In math, it's a problem. In history, it's a battle. In science, it's a reaction. But in my heart, it's you.
You are my universe.
The more people I meet, the more I realize that it's only you I want to be with.
I wouldn't mind waking up to your face everyday.
My first thought in the morning is always you.
Even if we can't be together in the end, I'm glad that you were a part of my life.
I don't care if there is someone better than you because to me you are the right one and the only one that I want.
When a girl says she's sad, but she isn't crying, it means she's crying in her heart.
One of the best feelings in the world is knowing your presence and absence both mean something to someone.
Are you a camera? Because everytime I look at you, I smile.
He's just a boy who doesn't understand what's in front of him. She's just a girl who doesn't know how to let go of him.
I've always wanted to be a princess. But now it's different, I want to be your princess.
We talked about the old times, which made me smile because you didn't forget.
I want someone who isn't afraid to be honest with me.
I wish I could hurt you the way you hurt me. But I know that if I had the chance, I wouldn’t do it.
It kinda sucks when you get in the habit of talking to someone every night. And then one night they're not there, everything gets so lonely.
It means everything when you message me first.
I promise I can be everything you want, if you give me a chance.
You should know, every time I smile or laugh, I'm secretly hoping you're watching.
I'm jealous of her. Not because of her looks, her personality or her material possessions. I'm jealous because she holds your attention.
When a girl is in love, you can see it in her smile. When a guy is in love, you can see it in his eyes.
Love is loving someone not just for the good things about them, but embracing their flaws and imperfections as well.
Love is when you tell after a fight that you don't want to talk but still checking your phone to see if he texted you.
I might hug other guys, I might laugh with other guys and I might text other guys, but none of them will ever mean as much to me as you do.
True love? Never dies.
I need someone who won't run away.
It's crazy what people do for love, and it's even crazier what love does to people.
I always wonder if you smile at my texts like I smile at yours.
I just want to have a place in your heart like you have a place in mine.
Within you, I lose myself. Without you, I find myself wanting to be lost again.
What hurts the most is seeing the person you love, loving someone else right in front of you.
It's the greatest feeling in the world to know that he couldn't let go of you either.
I know he's not the best guy in the world, but still there's something about him that makes my heart fall.
You're the smile to my face and the beat to my heart.
I am over you. I am over you. I am over you. I am over you. I am over you. Who am I kidding, I really want you.
You can't stay mad at someone who makes you smile.
Being deeply loved by someone gives you strength, while loving someone deeply gives you courage.
Love is like a piece of candy. You can buy it anywhere but given by the right person is what makes it special.
When his happiness is also your happiness, that's love.
It’s quite ironic that the person that brings the best in you and makes you strong is also your weakness.
It's been a long time since anyone has made me smile as much as you do.
I will always care about you, that's a fact. Even if we're not together and even if we are far, far away from each other.
I’m not here to make you cry, but to wipe away your tears. I’m not here to make you frown, but to turn that frown upside down.
I will always be yours, even when you don't want me.
Find someone who can make you laugh without even trying, who gives you butterflies everytime you two speak, who you can see a future with.
I may not be your first love, first kiss, first sight, or first date but I just want to be your last.
I don't want a relationship where people say, "They look so cute together." I want one where they say, "Look how happy they are together."
My love for you is a journey starting at forever and ending at never.
A girl’s worst nightmare is when the guy she loves stops doing the things that made her fall in love.
If only you knew, how happy you make me.
Forever’s a lie, everything’s temporary. But there are things you would be glad to fight for, so you have them longer.
I want us to stay strong. No matter how hard the situation is, no matter what or who comes between us.
When is the best time to tell someone you love them? Before someone else does.
There is always a soft spot in my heart for you. Even when you've done wrong, even when you've let me down, even when you didn't care.
Wanna keep your girl? Respect her, care for her, love her, text her first, make sure she knows how you feel about her and never lie.
I wish I could go back in time and find you sooner, that way I could love you longer.
Just the thought of being with you tomorrow is enough to get me through today.
Never let a girl feel that she’s not enough.
Any man can love a million girls, but only a real man can love one girl in a million ways.
You can’t have a relationship without any fights, but you can make your relationship worth the fight.
My day isn't complete without hearing your voice or getting a text from you.
I don’t need someone who will give me the world, I only need someone who will never leave no matter what.
It doesn't matter who hurt you, or broke you down, what matters is who made you smile again.
The strange thing about love is you don’t walk into it or run into it, you fall into it.
I love my eyes when you look at them. I love my name when you say it. I love my heart when you touch it. I love my life when you are in it.
My heart is, and always will be, yours.
I won't let you slip away and I won't let another person take my place.
She may be confused about a lot of things but she knows the only time she is truly happy is when she is with him.
Sometimes I wonder if love is worth fighting for, then I see your face and I am ready for the war.
Sometimes I just want to see my future to make sure you're in it.

Someday, someone is going to look at you like you're the most precious thing in the world.
Every love story is beautiful, but ours is my favorite.
It's really nice to have someone that makes you forget about all your problems.
I hope you never forget the first day that we started talking because that's when you and I began.
The one who is meant for you encourages you to be your best but still loves and accepts you at your worst.
I am really happy I met you, I hope you know that.
Some people can’t forget their first love, others can’t forget their last, the luckiest are those whose first love lasts.
Sometimes I lay in bed at night, and think about the things I wish I could say to you.
I enjoy making you smile. Just knowing that I’m the reason you smile, is enough for me.
When you go to bed, and he's all you can think about. You know you're falling in love.
In the end, I want to end up with you.
I want you.
If you like someone, tell them. There are over six billion people in this world, someone else might beat you to it.
I constantly wonder if I am on your mind as much as you're on mine.
I get butterflies just thinking about the next time I'll see you.
I still remember the feeling I felt when I first started talking to you.

For me there's only you.
A pure and lasting relationship has fights, has trust, has faith, has tears, has hurt, has laughter and has stupid unnecessary arguments.
I love the way you make me smile.
There are two reasons why I wake up in the morning: my alarm clock and you.
The best part of my day is spending time with you.
Just a simple "hi" from you is the highlight of my whole day.
I can live without you. But without you, I'll be miserable at best.
You don't walk in love, you fall in. That's why it is so hard to get out.
Every time I look at you, it’s like I’m falling for you all over again.
Yesterday I loved you the most I could love anyone, yet today I love you even more.
When a guy stares at you for long periods of time, he wishes you were his.
It actually kills me when we don't talk.
